  "prompt": "Where can I get a red coat, like Joaquin Phoenix used to wear in the movie Her, in India?",
  "response": "Finding a red coat similar to the one Joaquin Phoenix wore in *Her* can be a bit challenging, but here are some options to explore in India:\n\n### 1. **High-End Fashion Brands**\n   - **Zara**, **H&M**, **Uniqlo**, and **Marks & Spencer** often carry stylish overcoats in various colors, including red, especially during the winter season.\n   - **Tommy Hilfiger**, **Michael Kors**, and **Brooks Brothers** might also have similar trench or overcoat styles.\n\n### 2. **Custom Tailors**\n   - Visit a good tailor or boutique that specializes in custom menswear. Bring a picture of the coat from the movie to ensure they replicate the design, fabric, and fit.\n\n### 3. **Online Shopping Platforms**\n   - **Myntra**, **Ajio**, and **Amazon** often have a variety of overcoats in different shades of red. Filter your search by color and style.\n   - **Styleholic**, **Snitch**, and **Bewakoof** are Indian brands that might have trendy outerwear options.\n\n### 4. **Luxury and Designer Stores**\n   - Check stores like **Shoppers Stop**, **Lifestyle**, or **Pantaloons** for premium outerwear.\n   - Designer brands like **Rohit Bal**, **Tarun Tahiliani**, or **Sabyasachi** might have similar styles during their winter collections.\n\n### 5. **Second-Hand or Thrift Stores**\n   - Explore thrift stores or online platforms like **OLX**, **Quikr**, or **Instagram thrift stores** for vintage or pre-owned coats.\n\n### 6. **International Brands (Online)**\n   - If you\u2019re open to international shopping, check **ASOS**, **Farfetch**, or **Net-a-Porter** for designer overcoats.\n\n### 7. **Local Markets**\n   - Cities like Mumbai, Delhi, or Kolkata have wholesale markets (e.g., Colaba Causeway, Sarojini Nagar, New Market) where you might find affordable options.\n\n### Tips:\n- Look for a double-breasted, longline coat in a bright red shade.\n- Pay attention to the fabric\u2014wool or wool blends are ideal for a structured, elegant look.\n- Check the fit and length to match the cinematic style.\n\nHappy shopping! Let me know if you need more help.",
